  <div class="about-story-content">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <p>
        I'm currently a dual student of <strong>Computer Science (B.Sc.)</strong> and work as a <strong>Systems Engineer</strong>. This means I spend a lot of time with hardware, infrastructure, and various technical challenges. In my daily work and personal projects, I often encounter problems that aren't well documented online. Sometimes you just have to figure things out the hard way.
      </p>
      <p>
        This blog is mainly my personal notebook for technical problems and their solutions. When I finally get something working, I write it down here. If you stumble upon similar issues and find my notes helpful — <strong>great!</strong> That would make the extra effort of documenting everything worthwhile.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="about-quote">
        <p>Every problem solved is a lesson learned, and every lesson learned should be shared.</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
